 - Full challenge board\n - Full access to all modes\n - Full arsenal of 20+ firearms\n - Kamikaze drones\n - Augmented visor\n - Even more Tactical Tools\n - Both minigame floors\n - SimpleJack arcade cabinet\n - Facility induction\n - Progression system\n - Functional grievance booth\n - Big secret area, beyond the booth\n - More story / lore to uncover\n - Full 120 random announcements\n - Multiple save slots\n - Difficulty options\n - Permadeath option\n - New game plus\n - And even more!\n\nLooking for a tactical room clearing sim? A fast-paced action shooter? A casual, unusual, indie-game to explore? Shotwood has you covered! Grab this FREE demo right now and... SHOOT SOME WOOD!", "short_description": "FREE vertical slice demo of Shotwood. Smash deadly wooden targets with realistic firearms & explosives while you try to escape from this ominous, ridiculous, mysterious facility. Shotwood is the casual (yet satisfyingly tactical) shoot-house themed game!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/terms.html", "publisher_name": "Concrete Box", "support_website_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/support.html", "website_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3744040075834813"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE", "STANDING", "SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8077770712267033"}}]}, "scheduled_offers"